---
title: Chermoula Yoghurt Pork with Lemon & Roast Veggie Israeli Couscous
description: This meal is all about the little differences – the chermoula and yoghurt jazzing up the pork, the flavourful Israeli couscous
studded with chunks of sweet roasted veggies and the yoghurt drizzle that will become your new favourite accompaniment.

 *This recipe is under 650kcal per serving*
